    <item>
      <title>Citrix 母公司计划在市场创纪录的一年中修改第二笔贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/citrix-parent-aims-to-revise-second-loan-in-market-s-record-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citrix Systems Inc. 的母公司正在寻求在 2024 年进行第二次杠杆贷款重新定价，这是创纪录的一年，因为该市场交易额首次超过 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/citrix-parent-aims-to-revise-second-loan-in-market-s-record-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦克莱姆称加拿大央行必须“发现”中性利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/macklem-says-bank-of-canada-will-have-to-discover-neutral-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆对加拿大央行上周大幅降息的决定进行了更深入的分析，他表示，考虑到近年来央行大幅提高借贷成本以控制价格压力，此次降息是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/macklem-says-bank-of-canada-will-have-to-discover-neutral-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:52:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Barry 预计未来收益率曲线将进一步陡峭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/jpmorgan-s-barry-sees-steeper-yield-curves-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球利率策略主管杰伊·巴里 (Jay Barry) 表示，美国财政部目前状况良好。巴里在接受《彭博社收盘》采访时还对石油抛售发表了评论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/jpmorgan-s-barry-sees-steeper-yield-curves-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:47:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元流动性暴跌 72% 尼日利亚奈拉跌至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/naira-falls-to-record-low-after-dollar-liquidity-plunges-72</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于外汇市场美元流动性大幅下降，尼日利亚本币出现约两周来最大跌幅，跌至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/naira-falls-to-record-low-after-dollar-liquidity-plunges-72</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
