    <item>
      <title>法官承认对卡车司机 Yellow 65 亿美元养老金纠纷的裁决存在错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/judge-admits-error-in-ruling-on-bankrupt-trucker-yellow-s-pension-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官周一表示，法院的一项裁决可能使破产卡车公司 Yellow Corp. 股东的所有损失化为乌有，该裁决存在错误，可能需要推翻一项对该公司不利的关键决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/judge-admits-error-in-ruling-on-bankrupt-trucker-yellow-s-pension-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:35:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拍卖引发供应焦虑后，美国国债收益率恢复攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/treasury-yields-resume-climb-after-auctions-stir-supply-anxiety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券收益率上升，因为对一对美国国债拍卖的需求疲软表明投资者对下一个融资季度前夕的供应感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/treasury-yields-resume-climb-after-auctions-stir-supply-anxiety</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 18:17:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着伊朗风险消退，石油的重大期权押注变得毫无价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/oil-s-big-bullish-options-bets-turn-worthless-as-iran-risk-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[那些以创纪录的速度大举押注油价看涨期权的交易员们正在意识到一个残酷的现实：其中大多数合约现在都一文不值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/oil-s-big-bullish-options-bets-turn-worthless-as-iran-risk-fades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 17:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥航空启动 11 亿美元 2027 年票据再融资报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/aeromexico-starts-1-1-billion-offering-to-refinance-2027-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥航空公司集团 (Grupo Aeromexico SAB) 正在利用国际债务市场筹集高达 11 亿美元的资金，用于为现有票据进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/aeromexico-starts-1-1-billion-offering-to-refinance-2027-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司启动 190 亿美元股票出售计划，以阻止降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-boost-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司启动了一项近 190 亿美元的股票出售计划，这是上市公司历史上规模最大的股票出售计划之一，旨在解决这家陷入困境的飞机制造商的流动性需求，并避免其信用评级可能被下调至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-boost-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:54:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员制定选举计划，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在企业财报最为繁忙的一周开始时，股市上涨，交易员也在为美国大选和关键经济数据做准备，这些数据将为美联储下次决策奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
